{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda2fc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2884"},"text":"§ 2884.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reports","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda2fd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Project Reports","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda2fe-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary concerned shall transmit to the appropriate committees of Congress a report describing—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda2ff-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" each contract or agreement for the acquisition or construction of family housing units or unaccompanied housing units under this subchapter; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda300-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" each conveyance or lease proposed under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2878"},"text":"section 2878 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda301-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" A report required by paragraph (1) shall include the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda302-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A description of the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease, including a summary of the terms of the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda303-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A description of the authorities to be utilized in entering into the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease and the intended method of participation of the United States in the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease, including a justification of the intended method of participation.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda304-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A statement of the scored cost of the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease, as determined by the Office of Management and Budget.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda305-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/2/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A statement of the United States funds required for the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease and a description of the source of such funds, including a description of the specific construction, acquisition, or improvement projects from which funds were transferred to the Funds established under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2883"},"text":"section 2883 of this title","children":[],"tail":" in order to finance the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda306-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/2/E"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"E"},"text":"(E)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An economic assessment of the life cycle costs of the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease, including an estimate of the amount of United States funds that would be paid over the life of the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease from amounts derived from payments of government allowances, including the basic allowance for housing under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t37/s403"},"text":"section 403 of title 37","children":[],"tail":", if the housing affected by the project were fully occupied by military personnel over the life of the contract, agreement, conveyance, or lease."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda307-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda308-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" In the case of a contract or agreement described in paragraph (1) proposed to be entered into with a private party, the report shall specify whether the contract or agreement will or may include a guarantee (including the making of mortgage or rental payments) by the Secretary to the private party in the event of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda309-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/3/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the closure or realignment of the installation for which housing will be provided under the contract or agreement;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda30a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/3/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a reduction in force of units stationed at such installation; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda30b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/3/A/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the extended deployment of units stationed at such installation.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda30c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" If the contract or agreement will or may include such a guarantee, the report shall also—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda30d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/3/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" describe the nature of the guarantee; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda30e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/3/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" assess the extent and likelihood, if any, of the liability of the United States with respect to the guarantee.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda30f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/a/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The report shall be submitted in an electronic medium pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s480"},"text":"section 480 of this title","children":[],"tail":" not later than 21 days before the date on which the Secretary issues the contract solicitation or offers the conveyance or lease."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda310-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Annual Reports to Accompany Budget Materials","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Defense shall include each year in the materials that the Secretary submits to Congress in support of the budget submitted by the President pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1105"},"text":"section 1105 of title 31","children":[],"tail":" the following:"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda311-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A separate report on the expenditures and receipts during the preceding fiscal year covering each of the Funds established under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2883"},"text":"section 2883 of this title","children":[],"tail":", including a description of the specific construction, acquisition, or improvement projects from which funds were transferred and the privatization projects or contracts to which those funds were transferred. Each report shall also include, for each military department or defense agency, a description of all funds to be transferred to such Funds for the current fiscal year and the next fiscal year."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda312-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" A report setting forth, by armed force, the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda313-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An estimate of the amounts of basic allowance for housing under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t37/s403"},"text":"section 403 of title 37","children":[],"tail":" that will be paid, during the current fiscal year and the fiscal year for which the budget is submitted, to members of the armed forces living in housing provided under the authorities in this subchapter."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda314-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The number of units of military family housing and military unaccompanied housing upon which the estimate under subparagraph (A) for the current fiscal year and the next fiscal year is based.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda315-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" A description of the plans for housing privatization activities to be carried out under this subchapter—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda316-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" during the fiscal year for which the budget is submitted; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda317-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" during the period covered by the then-current future-years defense plan under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s221"},"text":"section 221 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda318-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A report identifying each family housing unit acquired or constructed under this subchapter that is used, or intended to be used, as quarters for a general officer or flag officer and for which the total operation, maintenance, and repair costs for the unit exceeded $50,000. For each housing unit so identified, the report shall also include the total of such operation, maintenance, and repair costs.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda319-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Semi-annual Report on Privatization Projects","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Defense shall submit to the congressional defense committees a semi-annual report containing an evaluation of the status of oversight and accountability measures under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2885"},"text":"section 2885 of this title","children":[],"tail":" for military housing privatization projects. To the extent each Secretary concerned has the right to attain the information described in this subsection, each report shall include, at a minimum, the following:"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda31a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of the backlog of maintenance and repair at each military housing privatization project where a significant backlog exists, including an estimation of the cost of eliminating the maintenance and repair backlog.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda31b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If the debt associated with a privatization project exceeds net operating income or the occupancy rates for the housing units are below 75 percent for more than one year, the plan developed to mitigate the financial risk of the project.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda31c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of any significant project variances between the actual and pro forma deposits in the recapitalization account, to specifically include any unique variances associated with litigation costs.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda31d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The details of any significant withdrawals from a recapitalization account, including the purpose and rationale of the withdrawal and, if the withdrawal occurs before the normal recapitalization period, the impact of the early withdrawal on the financial health of the project.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda31e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of the extent to which the information required to comply with paragraphs (1) through (4) has been requested by the Secretaries, but has not been made available.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda31f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of cost assessed to members of the armed forces for utilities compared to utility rates in the local area.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda320-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7"},"text":"(7)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of the condition of housing units based on the average age of those units and the estimated time until recapitalization.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda321-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/8"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8"},"text":"(8)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of tenant complaints.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda322-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9"},"text":"(9)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of maintenance response times and completion of maintenance requests.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda323-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/10"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"10"},"text":"(10)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of the dispute resolution process under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2894/c"},"text":"section 2894(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":", which shall include a list of dispute resolution cases by installation and the final outcome of each case."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda324-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/11"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"11"},"text":"(11)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of overall customer service for tenants.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda325-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/12"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"12"},"text":"(12)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A description of the results of any no-notice housing inspections conducted.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda326-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/13"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"13"},"text":"(13)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The results of any resident surveys conducted.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda327-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/14"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"14"},"text":"(14)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" With regard to issues of lead-based paint in housing units, a summary of data relating to the presence of lead-based paint in such housing units, including the following by military department:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda328-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/14/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The total number of housing units containing lead-based paint.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda329-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/14/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A description of the reasons for the failure to inspect any housing unit that contains lead-based paint.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda32a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/14/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A description of all abatement or mitigation efforts completed or underway in housing units containing lead-based paint.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda32b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/14/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A certification as to whether military housing under the jurisdiction of the Secretary concerned complies with requirements relating to lead-based paint, lead-based paint activities, and lead-based paint hazards, as described in section 408 of the Toxic Substances Control Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s2688"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 2688","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda32c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/15"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"15"},"text":"(15)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" An explanation of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda32d-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/15/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the housing data used by each Secretary concerned; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda32e-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/15/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the housing data each Secretary concerned requests from companies responsible for managing privatization projects.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda32f-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/16"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"16"},"text":"(16)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An assessment of how each Secretary concerned uses such housing data to inform the on-base housing decisions for the military department under the jurisdiction of the Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda330-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/17"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"17"},"text":"(17)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" An explanation of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda331-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/17/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the limitations of any tenant satisfaction data collected by the Secretary concerned (including limitations with respect to the availability of such data);","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda332-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/17/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the process of the Secretary concerned for determining tenant satisfaction; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda333-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/17/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" reasons for missing tenant satisfaction data, if any.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda334-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/18"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"18"},"text":"(18)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" To the maximum extent practicable, a breakdown of the information described in paragraphs (1) through (17), disaggregated by—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda335-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/18/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" military installation; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda336-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/c/18/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" military housing privatization project.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda337-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Annual Briefings","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than February 1 of each year, each Secretary concerned shall provide to the Committees on Armed Services of the Senate and House of Representatives a briefing on military housing privatization projects under the jurisdiction of the Secretary. Such briefing shall include, for the 12-month period preceding the date of the briefing, each of the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda338-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The information described in paragraphs (1) through (18) of subsection (c) of subsection (c) with respect to all military housing privatization projects under the jurisdiction of the Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda339-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A review of any such project that is expected to require the restructuring of a loan, including any public or private loan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda33a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" For any such project expected to require restructuring, a timeline for when such restructuring is expected to occur.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda33b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2884/d/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Such other information as the Secretary determines appropriate.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida9eda33c-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/106/dB/tXXVIII/s2801/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–106, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2801(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-02-10"},"text":"Feb. 10, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/550"},"text":"110 Stat. 550","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/136/dB/tXXVIII/s2807"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–136, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2807","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2003-11-24"},"text":"Nov. 24, 2003","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/117/1722"},"text":"117 Stat. 1722","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/375/dB/tXXVIII/s2806"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–375, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2806","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/2122"},"text":"118 Stat. 2122","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/163/dB/tXXVIII/s2806/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–163, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2806(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-01-06"},"text":"Jan. 6, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/119/3507"},"text":"119 Stat. 3507","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/417/dB/tXXVIII/s2805/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–417, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2805(b)","children":[],"tail":", (f), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-10-14"},"text":"Oct. 14, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/4723"},"text":"122 Stat. 4723","children":[],"tail":", 4724; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/383/dA/tX/s1075/h/6"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–383, div. A, title X,